@startuml Smart Policy Platform - Agent Architecture Flow

title Smart Policy Platform - Multi-Agent Architecture\n(Happy Path vs Complex Path with Manual Review)

actor "Applicant" as User
participant "Frontend\n(JavaScript)" as UI
participant "ApplicationController\n(Java)" as AppController
participant "QuoteAgentService\n(Java)" as QuoteService
participant "Quote Agent\n(Python/LangChain)" as QuoteAgent
participant "UnderwritingAgentService\n(Java)" as UWService
participant "Instant UW Agent\n(Python/LangChain)" as UWAgent
participant "EvidenceAgentService\n(Java)" as EvidenceService
participant "Evidence Agent\n(Python/LangChain)" as EvidenceAgent
participant "ManualUWAgentService\n(Java)" as ManualService
participant "Manual UW Agent\n(Python/LangChain)" as ManualAgent
participant "Human Underwriter\n(Admin Dashboard)" as Human
participant "StripePaymentService\n(Java)" as Payment
participant "PolicyIssuanceAgentService\n(Java)" as PolicyService
participant "Policy Issuance Agent\n(Python/LangChain)" as PolicyAgent
database "H2 Database" as DB

== STEP 1: Quote Generation (Both Paths) ==

User -> UI: Enter details\n(Age, Coverage, Health)
UI -> AppController: POST /api/quotes
AppController -> QuoteService: generateQuote(request)
QuoteService -> QuoteAgent: POST /agent/quote
note right of QuoteAgent
**Quote Agent Tools:**
- calculate_premium
- assess_risk_factors
- determine_eligibility
end note
QuoteAgent -> QuoteAgent: Calculate premium\nusing actuarial rules
QuoteAgent --> QuoteService: Quote + monthly premium
QuoteService -> DB: Save InsuranceQuote
QuoteService --> AppController: QuoteResponse
AppController --> UI: Quote details
UI --> User: Display quote

== STEP 2A: Happy Path - Instant Approval ==

note over User, DB #lightgreen
**HAPPY PATH CONDITIONS:**
- Age < 50
- Coverage < $500,000
- No serious medical conditions
end note

User -> UI: Submit Application
UI -> AppController: POST /api/applications
AppController -> UWService: performInstantUnderwriting()
UWService -> UWAgent: POST /agent/underwrite
note right of UWAgent
**Enhanced UW Agent:**
Rules Engine checks:
1. Coverage > $500k? ❌
2. Age > 50? ❌
3. Medical conditions? ❌
**Decision: INSTANT_APPROVE**
end note
UWAgent -> UWAgent: Run rules engine\nAll checks pass
UWAgent --> UWService: decision=APPROVE
UWService -> DB: Update status=APPROVED
UWService --> AppController: Approved response
AppController --> UI: Application approved
UI --> User: Show approval card

User -> UI: Make payment
UI -> AppController: POST /api/applications/{id}/payment
AppController -> Payment: createPaymentIntent()
Payment -> Payment: Stripe API call
Payment --> AppController: Payment Intent ID
AppController -> DB: Save payment intent
AppController --> UI: Client secret
UI -> User: Stripe Checkout
User -> Payment: Complete payment
Payment -> AppController: Webhook: payment_intent.succeeded
AppController -> PolicyService: issuePolicy()
PolicyService -> PolicyAgent: POST /agent/issue-policy
PolicyAgent -> PolicyAgent: Generate policy document
PolicyAgent --> PolicyService: Policy PDF + number
PolicyService -> DB: Save InsurancePolicy
PolicyService --> AppController: Policy issued
AppController --> UI: Policy details
UI --> User: Download policy

== STEP 2B: Complex Path - Manual Review Required ==

note over User, DB #lightyellow
**COMPLEX PATH TRIGGERS:**
- Age ≥ 50 OR
- Coverage ≥ $500,000 OR
- Medical conditions present
(e.g., Hypertension, Diabetes)
end note

User -> UI: Submit Application\n(Age: 55, Coverage: $750k,\nHealth: Hypertension)
UI -> AppController: POST /api/applications
AppController -> UWService: performInstantUnderwriting()
UWService -> UWAgent: POST /agent/underwrite

note right of UWAgent
**Enhanced UW Agent:**
Rules Engine detects:
✓ Age > 50 (55)
✓ Coverage > $500k ($750k)
✓ Medical condition (Hypertension)
**Decision: MANUAL_REVIEW**
end note

UWAgent -> UWAgent: Run rules engine\n3 flags triggered
UWAgent --> UWService: decision=MANUAL_REVIEW\nreasons=[age, coverage, health]
UWService -> DB: Update status=MANUAL_REVIEW_PENDING

== STEP 3: Evidence Collection (5-Second Simulation) ==

UWService -> EvidenceService: requestEvidence()
EvidenceService -> EvidenceAgent: POST /agent/request-evidence
note right of EvidenceAgent
**Evidence Agent Tools:**
- aps_request_tool (2 sec)
- medical_records_tool (1.5 sec)
- evidence_analysis_tool
Total: ~5 seconds simulation
end note
EvidenceAgent -> EvidenceAgent: Request APS documents\n(2-second delay)
EvidenceAgent -> EvidenceAgent: Request medical records\n(1.5-second delay)
EvidenceAgent -> EvidenceAgent: Generate mock evidence:\n- Physician notes\n- BP readings\n- Medication list
EvidenceAgent --> EvidenceService: Evidence data (5000 chars)
EvidenceService -> DB: Update evidenceData,\nstatus=EVIDENCE_COLLECTION
EvidenceService --> UWService: Evidence collected

== STEP 4: AI-Powered Manual Underwriting Analysis ==

UWService -> ManualService: analyzeEvidence()
ManualService -> ManualAgent: POST /agent/manual-underwrite\n(with evidence data)
note right of ManualAgent
**Manual UW Agent Tools:**
- evidence_analysis_tool
- risk_assessment_tool
AI extracts key findings
end note
ManualAgent -> ManualAgent: Extract findings:\n- "Controlled" condition\n- Medication compliance\n- Non-smoker
ManualAgent -> ManualAgent: Calculate risk rating:\nSTANDARD/MODERATE/HIGH
ManualAgent -> ManualAgent: Generate recommendation:\nAPPROVE_STANDARD\nAPPROVE_WITH_CONDITIONS\nREJECT
ManualAgent --> ManualService: Recommendation:\nAPPROVE_STANDARD\nRisk: MODERATE\nJustification (1000+ chars)
ManualService -> DB: Update:\n- agentRecommendation\n- riskRating=MODERATE\n- status=AWAITING_HUMAN_DECISION
ManualService --> UWService: Analysis complete
UWService --> AppController: All agent traces:\n1. Quote Agent\n2. Underwriting Agent\n3. Evidence Agent\n4. Manual UW Agent
AppController --> UI: Manual review response
UI --> User: Show Manual Review Pending Card:\n"Your application requires\nhuman underwriter review"

== STEP 5: Human Underwriter Decision (Future Implementation) ==

note over Human, DB #lightblue
**Admin Dashboard (To Be Built)**
Future endpoints:
- GET /admin/pending-reviews
- POST /admin/approve/{id}
- POST /admin/reject/{id}
end note

Human -> AppController: Login to admin dashboard
Human -> AppController: GET /admin/pending-reviews
AppController -> DB: Find applications\nwith status=AWAITING_HUMAN_DECISION
DB --> AppController: List of pending applications
AppController --> Human: Display:\n- Applicant details\n- Evidence summary\n- AI recommendation\n- Risk rating

alt Human Approves
    Human -> AppController: POST /admin/approve/{id}
    AppController -> DB: Update status=APPROVED\napprovedAt=now()
    AppController --> Human: Approval confirmed
    note right of Human
    Application proceeds to
    Payment → Policy Issuance
    (Same as Happy Path)
    end note
else Human Rejects
    Human -> AppController: POST /admin/reject/{id}\n(with reason)
    AppController -> DB: Update status=REJECTED\nunderwriterComments="reason"
    AppController --> Human: Rejection confirmed
    Human --> User: Send rejection notification
end

== Decision Points Summary ==

note over QuoteAgent, ManualAgent #lavender
**Agent Invocation Logic:**

1. **Quote Agent** (Python)
   - ALWAYS invoked for every request
   - Calculates premiums using actuarial tables

2. **Instant Underwriting Agent** (Python)
   - ALWAYS invoked for every application
   - Rules Engine decides path:
     * APPROVE → Happy Path (payment → policy)
     * REJECT → Application denied
     * MANUAL_REVIEW → Triggers Steps 3-5

3. **Evidence Agent** (Python)
   - CONDITIONAL: Only if UW decision = MANUAL_REVIEW
   - Simulates 5-second APS/medical records collection
   - Returns mock evidence data

4. **Manual Underwriting Agent** (Python)
   - CONDITIONAL: Only after Evidence Agent completes
   - AI-powered analysis of evidence
   - Provides recommendation for human

5. **Policy Issuance Agent** (Python)
   - CONDITIONAL: Only after payment completion
   - Generates policy PDF with terms
end note

legend right
|= Symbol |= Meaning |
| ❌ | Condition not met |
| ✓ | Condition triggered |
| → | Synchronous call |
| --> | Response |
endlegend

@enduml
